Accepted input formats:

  • DD/MM/YYYY (e.g., 01/01/1800)
  • DD-MM-YYYY (e.g., 01-01-1800)
  • DD.MM.YYYY (e.g., 01.01.1800)
  • DD MM YYYY (e.g., 01 01 1800)

    • Tips:

    • Use numbers only for Day, Month, and Year.
    • Ensure the date is valid (e.g., not February 30).

    By following these formats, you'll get the most accurate results from our date converter.
